<h2 id="org4214ddd">Workflow</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org4214ddd">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Open the Magit status buffer by running <code>M-x magit-status</code>. (<code>C-x g</code>)</li>
<li>Locate the untracked file in the "Untracked files" section.</li>
<li>Press <code>k</code> (for "kill") while the cursor is on the untracked file.</li>
<li>Confirm</li>
<li>can delete braches with <code>b k</code></li>
</ul>
